  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - Got word already from my guy you spoke to earlier.
  - "But just so you know, I can\u2019t stand people like you, only thing you care
    about is your little \u201Cfamily\u201D  and all the adjacent bullshit."
  - "Everyone in this fucking town is obsessed with it, you wanna go out or do anything
    ? It\u2019s always meeting people, seeing friends, finding a partner, making
    a family."
  - Someone like me? Government gives nothing, no place, no purpose, no anything.
  - "But whatever, you\u2019re willing to cooperate so you\u2019re better than most
    at least/"
  - 'You: Oh, thank you. I hope I can be of good help.'
  - Sure, yeah.
  - "Anyways, I\u2019ll get you up to speed, y\u2019know those symptom hiding rumours?"
  - "Yeah, we\u2019ve got no hard proof yet, but I\u2019ll tell you one thing, there\u2019s
    more to it than just that."
  - "All these bullshit decisions and announcements that they\u2019re making are
    part of their plan, and they\u2019ve got more hidden than you can even imagine."
  - "That\u2019s all, expect messages later, we\u2019ll have things for you to do."
